<div class='hero-unit'>
  <h1>
    <%= 'A better way to carpool to school!'.titleize %>
  </h1>
  <ul>
    <li>
    <span class='lead'>
      Need help transporting your kids? Find a fellow parent to drive them!
    </span>
    </li>
    <li>
    <span class='lead'>Willing to drive other kids and make some money along the way? Find a fellow parent who's happy to share the cost!</span>
